data.description: Welcome to Your Private Oasis. Pristine 3Bedroom 2Bathroom 2Car Garage Private POOL Home with Screened Porch & RV/Boat Pad. All TILE Flooring. Split Floor Plan. Primary Suite with Large Walk In Closet, Sliders to Porch/Pool, Private Bath with Tiled Walk-In Shower & Dual Sink Vanity. Salt System Pool, Custom Surf Outdoor Shower, Cabana Bath, Lush Landscaping & Fenced Backyard. 2017 Metal Roof, 2016 AC & 13mo HWA Home Warranty. Transferable Termite Bond.
